                                                 Read me
  This patch is used to apply to openssl-0.9.8.tar.gz, which can be downloaded from:http://www.openssl.org.Please use the exact package name, otherwise it is possible the patch can be some problem.

  After unzip the tarball:

  tar zxf openssl-0.9.8.tar.gz

  patch -p0 < libssl_bfin_patch

  rm -rf /your/uClinux/path/lib/libssl

  mv openssl-0.9.8 /your/uClinux/path/lib/libssl



  
